# Student Registry — Python Assignment

Project description

This is a small university assignment implemented in Python. The program collects student records (name, student ID, age, and major) and stores them in a Python dictionary. The project demonstrates basic data structures, simple input/output, and common operations such as adding, updating, removing, and listing student entries.

